to Washington or New York.

01:16:38.761 --> 01:16:41.263
I was 42 before I won my first campaign.

01:16:44.934 --> 01:16:46.768
And I'm happy for all of y'all.

01:16:49.689 --> 01:16:52.440
You've been part of
something special in my life.

01:16:57.947 --> 01:16:59.614
[Camera Shutter Clicks]

01:17:00.908 --> 01:17:03.285
