Oh, God.

01:21:31.762 --> 01:21:34.222
- Our prayers and our hopes for a better America.
- Shut up.

01:21:35.391 --> 01:21:37.058
Throughout this campaign,
I've endeavored...

01:21:37.142 --> 01:21:39.143
to bring my message
of change to the American people.

01:21:39.228 --> 01:21:40.979
[Bob] Where's Derek Humphry
when you need him?

01:21:41.063 --> 01:21:43.106
