01:26:52.583 --> 01:26:53.875
No Busch beer.

01:26:55.043 --> 01:26:56.544
Landslide.

01:26:57.129 --> 01:27:01.716
[Laughing]

01:27:02.926 --> 01:27:06.053
[Cheering]

01:27:07.472 --> 01:27:09.390
Pennsylvania!

